                    <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Taylor</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Gresham</persName></hi>.</head>
                    <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Madrid</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-12-30"><hi rend="italic">December 30,
                            1893</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                    <p>Very encouraging interview yesterday—details mailed.</p>
                    <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Taylor.</hi></signed></closer>
